{"TopicId":193204,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Are you growing a quarantine beard?","CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T20:20:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T20:20:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnswer the question!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T21:20:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772440\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587154812\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n58 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnswer the question!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI still do video conferencing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA beard is not an option. I also still work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSaint","CreatedById":70033,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T21:52:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo. Although I\u0027m shaving less than I used to. Because the only thing I hate worse than shaving is having a beard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T21:54:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope. I\u2019m still shaving.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T22:14:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can see mine when I stream on Sunday and Monday night\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IncongruousGoat","CreatedById":157062,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T22:19:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI keep on getting close, and then chickening out and shaving it. So, sort of?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-17T23:41:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. If the quarantine goes on long enough I will get creative with plaits and beeswax.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T01:09:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope, can\u0027t wear a mask with a beard. I also look better sans beard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T01:29:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot really.\u00A0 My response has been to run clippers over my whole head once a week for a nice uniform finish.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T04:39:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo. It doesn\u0027t fit in the spacesuit helmet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso its hair is bad for the air filters.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-18T09:41:55Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2020 09:41  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T05:08:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m actually shaving more often. Mostly because I used to shave on Fridays and now I don\u0027t have a schedule so I shave whenever I feel like it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Elthy","CreatedById":63317,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T07:21:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm trying to grow one xD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T09:44:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E(Two weeks later, thread renamed)\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022How many hairs are there in your quarantine beard?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T14:12:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni already had one but its reached new levels of bushiness.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni usually let it grown out in the fall and winter months and trim it down to a goatee the rest of the year. but with the late ending winter and the virus i just don\u0027t see any point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772620\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587194501\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002263317\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Elthy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Elthy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm trying to grow one xD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nprotip for growing beards:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nturn 30. went\u00A0and done a hard flip from wont grow at all to wont stop growing around that time. for me this all happened around 30 and has only got worse since,\u00A0but ymmv.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772472\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587158431\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI still do video conferencing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA beard is not an option. I also still work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni live in a fishing town populated by people of viking ancestry\u00A0so a beard is standard workplace equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-18T14:21:33Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2020 02:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Nuke\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T14:41:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E, what about you?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow can you be left so\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eeasily?\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T14:43:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill shave. I shave my head (been doing this for 20 years) and still have the moustache and goatee.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nKinda like my avatar. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0026lt;---\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T16:20:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah. I never was much good at growing them in the first place and now they just come through in salt-and-pepper which is not a good look. With that said, its nice to only have to shave every second or third day rather than every day.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-18T16:20:49Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2020 04:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by KSK\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T16:22:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWent for a Karl Marx, ended up with a Fidel Castro. Shaved it off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T16:25:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587226921\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167629\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brikoleur\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Brikoleur said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWent for a Karl Marx, ended up with a Fidel Castro. Shaved it off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002218885b92ac476c75f0f9ae4b16ce2f40.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022123.41\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 width=\u0022622\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.pinimg.com/originals/18/88/5b/18885b92ac476c75f0f9ae4b16ce2f40.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T16:50:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen KSP-2 comes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221382475559.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002268.29\u0022 height=\u0022280\u0022 width=\u0022410\u0022 src=\u0022https://img.likeness.ru/14/86/14862/1382475559.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T17:49:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t like having a beard because mine grows bushy and never looks tidy no matter how carefully I trim it, but I\u0027ve been curious to see how much gray is in it now and the quarantine seemed like a good time to find out. (It\u0027s mostly gray.)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T18:53:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772726\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587221034\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GDJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, GDJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill shave. I shave my head (been doing this for 20 years) and still have the moustache and goatee.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nKinda like my avatar. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0026lt;---\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntried the cueball look in highschool, found out my head is too bumpy for it to look good. ended up developing a scalp condition that made me look like one of the aliens from alien nation. as a result my hair is now 3 feet long.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T20:00:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772767\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587226921\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167629\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brikoleur\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Brikoleur said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWent for a Karl Marx,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should have gone for the Groucho.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022060257f5263a4d2e01fd68b23369973a.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022122.00\u0022 height=\u0022488\u0022 width=\u0022400\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.pinimg.com/originals/06/02/57/060257f5263a4d2e01fd68b23369973a.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-18T23:55:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772714\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587219135\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni already had one but its reached new levels of bushiness.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni usually let it grown out in the fall and winter months and trim it down to a goatee the rest of the year. but with the late ending winter and the virus i just don\u0027t see any point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nprotip for growing beards:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nturn 30. went\u00A0and done a hard flip from wont grow at all to wont stop growing around that time. for me this all happened around 30 and has only got worse since,\u00A0but ymmv.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni live in a fishing town populated by people of viking ancestry\u00A0so a beard is standard workplace equipment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will have a hard time suppressing laughter the day I see this...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d6h4ti1-62ea446f-e31b-4a00-88e8-50fa5d25\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022133.33\u0022 height=\u0022768\u0022 width=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/a1feb18c-04db-4cb3-be55-61b4faf5ece7/d6h4ti1-62ea446f-e31b-4a00-88e8-50fa5d25304a.png?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..4cFRqhWEH0G9mN9wRSW02BFKhNu_N_tE-Fbq9YQDFXs\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGranted... these guys likely wore beard extension wigs... but still.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly kings can get away looking this ridiculous.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBack in the day it was considered fashionable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it will make a comeback?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-19T13:26:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223772822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221587236023\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210883\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nuke\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Nuke said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntried the cueball look in highschool, found out my head is too bumpy for it to look good. ended up developing a scalp condition that made me look like one of the aliens from alien nation. as a result my hair is now 3 feet long.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt took a while for me to get used to it. Ironically I tend to leave a tiny bit of stubble on during the summertime. It\u0027s cooler due to sweating and wicking away (hence better evaporation and cooling).\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso helps keeping the toque on in winter. Otherwise it slides off.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nBUT.....it\u0027s far cheaper to buy razorblades than going to the barber.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}